729001f-a.title: Richmond: Hylan Boulevard - Old Town Road
729001f-a.text:
Hylan Boulevard, at the N.W. corner of Old Town Road, showing
the 'Villa Tocci'. The house is 100 feet back of the road.
April 22, 1932.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

729260f-a.title: Richmond: Old Town Road - Hylan Boulevard
729260f-a.text:
O1d Town Road, south side, between Hylan Boulevard and
Oregon Road, showing the Garretson House, part of which dates
to colonial days. In 1874 it belonged to W.W. McFarland; from
1898 to 1907 to Rumpf, and in 1917 to M.M. Rutman.
1924
P. L. Sperr
